<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٧٠٢)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ شَبِيبُ بْنُ الْبَرْصَاءِ الْمُرِّيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ - وَإِنِّي لَتَرَّاكُ الضَّغِينَةِ قَدْ أَرَى ... قَذَاهَا مِنَ الْمَوْلَى فَلا أَسْتَثِيرُهَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢ - مخَافَةَ أَنْ تَجَنِي عَلَيَّ وَإِنَّمَا ... يَهِيجُ كَبِيرَاتِ الأُمُورِ صَغِيرُهَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٧٠٣)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ يَزِيدُ بْنُ الْحَكَمِ:</span> <span class="c2">(مجزوء الكامل)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - اِعْلَمْ بَنيَّ فَإِنَّهُ ... بِالْعِلْمِ يَنْتَفِعُ الْعَلِيمُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢ - أنَّ الأُمُورَ دَقِيقُهَا ... مِمَّا يَهِيجُ لَهُ الْعَظِيمُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧٠٤)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ مِسْكِينُ بْنُ عَامِرٍ الدَّارِمِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(مجزوء الكامل)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١ - وَلقَدْ رَأَيْتُ الشَّرَّ بَيْـ ... ـنَ النَّاسِ يَبْعَثُهُ صِغَارُهْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢ - فَلَوَ انَّهُمْ يَأْسُونَهُ ... لَتَنَهْنَهَتْ عَنْهُمْ كِبَارُهْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٧٠٥)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عُبَيْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْمَدَانِ الْحَارِثيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>١ - ألَمْ تَعْلَمَا يَا ابْنَيْ أُمَامَةَ إِنَّمَا ... يَهِيجُ كَبيرَاتِ الأُمورِ صِغَارُهَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>